d sexual assault|website=MassLive|location=Worcester, Massachusetts|date=2019-06-21|access-date=2019-07-09|archive-date=2022-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121030250/https://www.masslive.com/capecod/2019/06/help-me-court-filings-in-kevin-spacey-case-show-text-messages-accuser-sent-during-alleged-sexual-assault.html}}</ref>。2019年6月4日，辩方了解到，2017年烏拉将儿子的手机交给警方时，承认自己已经删除了一些短信<ref name="masslive"/>。当月晚些时候，她的儿子对史派西提起诉讼，声称受到精神损害。2019年7月5日，他自愿撤诉<ref>{{cite web|first1=Dakin|last1=Andone|first2=Jean|last2=Casarez|url=https://www.cnn.com/2019/07/05/us/kevin-spacey-lawsuit-dropped/index.html|title=The man who accuses Kevin Spacey of groping him dropped his civil lawsuit against the actor|website=[[CNN|CNN]]|publisher=[[Turner_Broadcasting_Systems|Turner Broadcasting Systems]]|location=Atlanta, Georgia|date=2019-07-05|access-date=2019-07-09|archive-date=2021-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108213840/https://www.cnn.com/2019/07/05/us/kevin-spacey-lawsuit-dropped/index.html}}</ref>。

